item.title: [317 delta] how to change the cords where you start[317 delta]
item.dc:creator: @SandScape SandScape
item.description:
@SandScape wrote:

[quote=“x blitz x, post:6, topic:260026”][quote author=SandScape link=topic=343331.msg2652174#msg2652174 date=1233597315]

When you log in, find the coords.
Open player.java and press ctrl+f
Type in the X coord, and only the X.
Then change that, and it should say:

TeleporttoX= #### TeleporttoY= ####
change it to what you want.
[/quote]searched in player.java so many times

Then you fail at searching lol.
Search [quote]
// the first call to updateThisPlayerMovement() will craft the proper initialization packet
[/quote]
and if you can’t find that search for the constructer.

public Player(int _playerId)

It’s inside that.[/quote]ok that worked thnx blitz
